[helv 14;bd]Section VIII
City Desk Reference Guide
[roman 10;pl;fj]


   The following section is the C‚i‚t‚y‚ ‚D‚e‚s‚k‚ Reference Guide. This section covers all menus on a command by command basis. You will find the Reference Guide useful for quick review of commands once you've become familiar with the typesetting terminology and the menus in C‚i‚t‚y‚ ‚D‚e‚s‚k‚.
   Command keys for each menu option are provided to speed up the selection process. These keys are activated by holding down the right (A)miga key and pressing the  selected letter.


