"Edit Page Format" is also activated by holding down the right (A)miga key and pressing the letter "X" at the same time.


EDIT
    Reflow Text Chain    (A) R

    "Reflow Text Chain" redisplays (or reformats) text on the page. It is useful when a new graphic is introduced or a graphic has been resized so text may reflow around them.


EDIT
    Invert Graphic       (A) I

    This option is like taking the negative of a  picture. The colors in the picture are turned from black to white or from white to black. It becomes useful when you want to give the figure a background against the page.



